    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
    Try asking 3-4 different questions from different categories to get a full sense of the chatbot's capabilities.
  </strong>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Questions to ask yourself</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">As you try these questions, consider:</p>

<div class="govuk-accordion" data-module="govuk-accordion" id="evaluation-accordion">
  <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
    <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
      <h3 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
        <span class="govuk-accordion__section-button" id="accordion-heading-1">
          For service managers
        </span>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div id="accordion-content-1" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-heading-1" hidden>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>Which of these questions do you get most often in your call centre?</li>
        <li>Would residents be satisfied with these responses?</li>
        <li>What percentage of your call volume could this handle?</li>
        <li>Which services would benefit most from 24/7 AI support?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
    <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
      <h3 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
        <span class="govuk-accordion__section-button" id="accordion-heading-2">
          For technical staff
        </span>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div id="accordion-content-2" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-heading-2" hidden>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>How accurate are the responses compared to your knowledge base?</li>
        <li>How would you integrate this with existing systems (CRM, case management)?</li>
        <li>What data sources would you connect to make this production-ready?</li>
        <li>How would you handle edge cases or unusual questions?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
    <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
      <h3 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
        <span class="govuk-accordion__section-button" id="accordion-heading-3">
          For leadership
        </span>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div id="accordion-content-3" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-heading-3" hidden>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>What's the business case for implementing this?</li>
        <li>What are the risks (accuracy, data protection, public perception)?</li>
        <li>What resources would we need to deploy this in production?</li>
        <li>How would we measure success and ROI?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

